ActIndian Act
SubjectMistawasis Indian Reserve No. 103G, Saskatchewan ** Grant of Easement **
PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise by SASKATCHEWAN POWER CORPORATION of the power to take an interest in lands within MISTAWASIS INDIAN RESERVE NO. 103G, located approximately 70 kilometers west of Prince Albert, Saskatchewan; and (b) granting the Company the required easement.
